snippet.title: Quickly, Quackley! early teaser (Jan 2021)
snippet.description:
Quackley the duck needs to get a job, and, OH QUACK! THERE'S ONLY 13 SECONDS LEFT TO GET TO THE INTERVIEW!

High-speed, ZX Spectrum-styled, precision platforming with a quirky sense of humour and authentic '80s style -- we had best start quacking and get this bread!
